Background

		Mr. Garrett E. Pierce has been the Chief Financial Officer of Orbital ATK, Inc. (formerly known as Alliant Techsystems Inc.) since February 9, 2015. Mr. Pierce served as the Chief Financial Officer and Executive Vice President of Orbital Sciences Corp. from August 2000 to April 2002. From 1996 to August 2000, he served as the Chief Financial Officer and Executive Vice President of Sensormatic Electronics Corp. where he served as the Chief Administrative Officer since ... July 1998. He served as the Chief Financial Officer and Executive Vice President of California Microwave Inc. From 1980 to 1993, Mr. Pierce served at Materials Research Corporation, where he served as the Chief Financial Officer, President and Chief Executive Officer. Mr. Pierce has been the Chairman of Kulicke and Soffa Industries, Inc. since September 28, 2014. He has been Vice Chairman of Orbital Sciences Corp. since April 2002. From 1972 to 1980, he served various management positions at the Signal companies. Mr. Pierce has been a Director of Orbital Sciences Corp. since August 2000. Mr. Pierce has been a Director of Kulicke and Soffa Industries, Inc. since December 1, 2005.Read Full Background




